    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "Illustrated identification key to females of the genus Sabethes Robineau-Desvoidy recorded from Brazil (Diptera: Culicidae), in dichotomous and interactive formats, including an updated list of species and new records for the states" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618244>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618246>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618248>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618250>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618258>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618252>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618254>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10618256> ;
